{"tid":766891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞司機揸車用電話遭票控不滿與差佬對罵，途人勸交變打交齊被捕","createTime":"2018-08-04T04:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T05:23:17.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"775e1a3c2d5bebe4ca99d86afcaed14fdc57738f","tid":766891,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"周五(3日)下午3時許，交通警員於長沙灣道194號對開，發現一名38歲南亞男子駕駛時使用手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，遂將其截擬停票控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，司機聞言情緖激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不斷指罵交警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一名43歲金毛男途人見狀不值司機所為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，上前理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，雙方初則口角繼而動武<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n二人糾纏期間，男途人曾多次表示：「呢度係香港嚟，差人你都打！」交警雖然手持伸縮警棍嘗試分隔兩人，但無果，只好通知上峰增援，並稱「有一名見義勇為嘅市民衝咗出嚟。」大批市民在場圍觀，未幾多名PTU警員接報趕至維持秩序，並將涉案兩名男子拘捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 涉嫌於公眾地方打架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，帶返警署扣查<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180804/58520874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F58520874&d=OyPra5W0UsMmW4Xh8JxRCIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4bf316f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F58520874&h=3bf58151\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180804/58520874</a>"},{"pid":"0fd5ab017a5d1ad6ac4bf37b3a1abc94a3f80e3b","tid":766891,"uid":119769,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"reply